      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NANGAR NUGGET (5) is progressing well with another good run last time, placing (28.37) last time out at this track. Goes very well here finding the frame in each of three starts. Can find winning form. MISS NO SHOW (1) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by 3.5 lengths at this track in a handy 28.11 beating JAVEN'S SHOT. Winner at her latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Capable of going well again. INTEGRITY MARNA (3) last start finished 3rd on February 24 over 484m at this track behind RUDOLF RUMBLE beaten 6 lengths (28.33) in a Grade 5. Looks suited here and can measure up. LEE FITZ (2) was in the money again last start when second at this track (28.11).",
